Info.Title: Harry Potter and the Order of the Phoenix
Info.Actors: Daniel Radcliffe, Harry Melling, Jason Boyd, Richard Macklin
Info.Plot: With their warning about Lord Voldemort's (Ralph Fiennes') return scoffed at, Harry (Daniel Radcliffe) and Dumbledore (Sir Michael Gambon) are targeted by the Wizard authorities as an authoritarian bureaucrat slowly seizes power at Hogwarts.
Info.Awards: Nominated for 2 BAFTA Film Awards. Another 14 wins & 40 nominations.
